Kosmas (Amụrụ n'ọnwa Febụwarị 25, 1944) bụ onye bụbu onye nnọchi anya US maka mpaghara nke iri abụọ na anọ nke Florida, na-eje ozi otu oge site n'afọ 2009 ruo afọ 2011
Ọ bụ onye otu Democratic Party
Ọ rụburu ọrụ na Florida House of Representatives.
Kosmas ebiela na New Smyrna Beach kemgbe afọ 1973
O nweela Prestige Properties nke New Smyrna Beach, ụlọ ọrụ ụlọ, kemgbe afọ 1979
Kosmas gara Mahadum Pennsylvania State na Mahadum George Mason, mgbe e mesịrị gụsịrị akwụkwọ Phi Beta Kappa na Mahadim Stetson n'afọ 1998.
